{"tid":2511780,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"其實 警察 都係公務員黎","createTime":"2021-05-01T07:22:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-01T07:39:54.000Z","uid":18679,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e7b10e21934e4efce941968896931782d9986ea9","tid":2511780,"uid":18679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T07:22:56.000Z","msg":"辛辛苦苦過咗學堂<br />\n<br />\n每日比唔同人屌老豆老母<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"purple\">就係為咗日日比人話做狗</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人返工你返工 你每日就要戴狗牌著狗衫<br />\n<br />\n返屋企又要斯斯縮縮<br />\n<br />\n你老母臭大你連講自己子女做咩職業都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我話你聽<br />\n<br />\n我每朝一起身睇完呢個gif 笑到醒咗返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWyccwf38rt2jyd5UsKe9CA3avy5h4hmKRdri3tLTSBKJ?filename=a1azdCx.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa1azdCx.gif&h=188d5498&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n51勞動節 慢慢捱啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f0d2b20cff85e9076433c5fcad2df06f2a5a102","tid":2511780,"uid":79793,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T07:23:56.000Z","msg":"張gif好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e0443ab4f657c338a60bceb72bf2c73adba0b56","tid":2511780,"uid":341884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep